r-be-reined-in/0000018d-ebc0-d401-a3dd-ebda30fd0000</guid></item><item><title>战争中的以色列：您需要了解的信息 – 第 144 天</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-02-27/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-what-you-need-to-know-day-144/0000018d-eb6f-d401-a3dd-eb7f2a0f0000</link><description>拜登：如果达成释放人质/停火协议，以色列愿意在斋月期间停止加沙战斗，希望下周一能达成协议 ■ 一位以色列高级消息人士告诉美国广播公司新闻，内塔尼亚胡总理对拜登的言论感到惊讶 ■ 哈马斯官员称该组织正在研究巴黎制定的最新提案，但双方之间仍存在巨大差距 ■ 这是战争开始 144 天后您需要了解的内容</description><pubDate>Tue, 27 Feb 2024 16:46:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-02-27/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-what-you-need-to-know-day-144/0000018d-eb6f-d401-a3dd-eb7f2a0f0000</guid></item><item><title>拜登可以依靠这两位以色列政客作为他的盟友吗？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-27/ty-article/.premium/can-biden-depend-on-these-two-israeli-politicians-to-be-his-allies/0000018d-eacb-d7f4-a3dd-eecfb42b0000</link><description>本尼·甘茨和加迪·艾森科特加入了以色列战时内阁，忙于减少错误决策并防止鲁莽决策。但他们现在会支持拜登对加沙和该地区的愿景，还是成为内塔尼亚胡的全职帮凶？</description><pubDate>Tue, 27 Feb 2024 16:02:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-27/ty-article/.premium/can-biden-depend-on-these-two-israeli-politicians-to-be-his-allies/0000018d-eacb-d7f4-a3dd-eecfb42b0000</guid></item><item><title>对于流离失所的以色列青少年来说，荒野是寻找自我的完美场所</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-27/ty-article-magazine/.premium/for-displaced-israeli-teens-the-wilderness-is-proving-a-perfect-place-to-find-themselves/0000018d-ea2a-dc4b-a1cd-fb2f759e0000</link><description>约20万以色列人因战争而被疏散，青少年在孤立、焦虑和抑郁中挣扎。一项新举措旨在帮助他们逃离大自然</description><pubDate>Tue, 27 Feb 2024 15:08:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-27/ty-article-magazine/.premium/for-displaced-israeli-teens-the-wilderness-is-proving-a-perfect-place-to-find-themselves/0000018d-ea2a-dc4b-a1cd-fb2f759e0000</guid></item><item><title>因恐怖袭击而在以色列服无期徒刑的巴勒斯坦作家获得阿拉伯文学最高奖提名</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2024-02-27/ty-article/.premium/palestinian-writer-jailed-in-israel-for-bombing-is-nominated-for-top-arab-literature-prize/0000018d-eab9-dc4b-a1cd-fbbdd23b0000</link><description>出生于纳布卢斯的巴森·卡达吉 (Basem Khadaqji) 于 2005 年因协助一名在特拉维夫杀害三名以色列人的自杀式炸弹袭击者而被定罪，在手稿被偷运出狱后，他在狱中出版了至少六本书</description><pubDate>Tue, 27 Feb 2024 14:43:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2024-02-27/ty-article/.premium/palestinian-writer-jailed-in-israel-for-bombing-is-nominated-for-top-arab-literature-prize/0000018d-eab9-dc4b-a1cd-fbbdd23b0000</guid></item><item><title>右翼 MKs 不顾专业人士的意见，通过新法律扩大本·格维尔的权力</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-27/ty-article/.premium/far-right-mks-moving-to-extend-ben-gvirs-authority-with-new-law/0000018d-ea6c-d409-a1ff-ef7eb62d0000</link><description>根据该提案，国家安全部长将能够宣布一群人为犯罪组织，并让他们没收资产。司法部警告该法律将过多权力集中于一个政府机构</description><pubDate>Tue, 27 Feb 2024 14:26:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-27/ty-article/.premium/far-right-mks-moving-to-extend-ben-gvirs-authority-with-new-law/0000018d-ea6c-d409-a1ff-ef7eb62d0000</guid></item><item><title>警方正在寻找周日以来失踪的以色列北部 9 岁女孩</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-27/ty-article/.premium/police-searching-for-nine-year-old-girl-from-northern-israel-missing-since-sunday/0000018d-ea56-dc4b-a1cd-fb7fceaa0000</link><description>三年前从埃塞俄比亚移民的海马诺特·卡绍(Haimanot Kassau)最后一次被人看见是在她居住的吸收中心的入口处。警方已收集安全录像和证词，但目前尚未找到任何线索</description><pubDate>Tue, 27 Feb 2024 13:33:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-27/ty-article/.premium/police-searching-for-nine-year-old-girl-from-northern-israel-missing-since-sunday/0000018d-ea56-dc4b-a1cd-fb7fceaa0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列135,000名流离失所公民的悲剧</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-27/ty-article-magazine/.premium/what-makes-the-plight-of-israels-displaced-citizens-different/0000018d-ea95-d1e0-a1dd-fbf529ed0000</link><description>由于加沙战争，来自北方和南方的以色列人发现自己在自己的国家内流离失所，而且看不到任何明确的解决方案。 《国土报》采访了流离失所问题专家，了解其带来的挑战</description><pubDate>Tue, 27 Feb 2024 13:29:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-27/ty-article-magazine/.premium/what-makes-the-plight-of-israels-displaced-citizens-different/0000018d-ea95-d1e0-a1dd-fbf529ed0000</guid></item><item><title>公共广播公司坎删除了以色列柏林电影节获奖者演讲反犹太主义标签的片段</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-27/ty-article/.premium/israels-public-broadcaster-removes-accusations-of-antisemitism-against-berlinale-winner/0000018d-ea27-d7f4-a3dd-ee2f193d0000</link><description>以色列电影导演尤瓦尔·亚伯拉罕的获奖感言提到了约旦河西岸受压迫的巴勒斯坦人，公共广播公司 Kan 称其为“反犹太主义”。亚伯拉罕的律师表示，自演讲发表以来，亚伯拉罕“收到了无数的威胁、死亡愿望和诅咒”</description><pubDate>Tue, 27 Feb 2024 13:07:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-27/ty-article/.premium/israels-public-broadcaster-removes-accusations-of-antisemitism-against-berlinale-winner/0000018d-ea27-d7f4-a3dd-ee2f193d0000</guid></item><item><title>前以色列国防军副司令亚伊尔·戈兰将竞选工党领袖</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-27/ty-article/.premium/former-idf-chief-yair-golan-to-run-for-labor-party-leadership/0000018d-ea3a-d05b-addd-eebbf79e0000</link><description>这位前梅雷茨议员因10月7日勇敢的救援行动而声名鹊起，他正准备参加初选，以取代现任工党领袖梅拉夫·米凯利，打算“建立一个新的政治框架，团结整个自由派阵营”</description><pubDate>Tue, 27 Feb 2024 12:25:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-27/ty-article/.premium/former-idf-chief-yair-golan-to-run-for-labor-party-leadership/0000018d-ea3a-d05b-addd-eebbf79e0000</guid></item><item><title>拜登表示以色列已准备好暂停加沙战斗；哈马斯称协议尚未完成</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-27/ty-article/biden-says-israel-is-ready-to-pause-gaza-fighting-hamas-says-deal-not-done-yet/0000018d-e991-d9a9-a1bd-ebbb67a00000</link><description>以色列代表团周一抵达卡塔尔继续会谈，美国总统乔·拜登在斋月之前公开设定下周在加沙达成停火协议的最后期限。然而，哈马斯否认已达成协议</description><pubDate>Tue, 27 Feb 2024 11:36:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-27/ty-article/biden-says-israel-is-ready-to-pause-gaza-fighting-hamas-says-deal-not-done-yet/0000018d-e991-d9a9-a1bd-ebbb67a00000</guid></item><item><title>为什么以色列不后悔自己从未支持乌克兰对抗俄罗斯</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-27/ty-article/.premium/why-israel-isnt-sorry-it-never-stood-by-ukraine-against-russia/0000018d-e623-d7f4-a3dd-e62f0fdb0000</link><description>尽管俄罗斯加入了针对以色列的伊朗-哈马斯-真主党轴心，但以色列同意向乌克兰提供军事援助的可能性比以前更小了</description><pubDate>Tue, 27 Feb 2024 10:31:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-27/ty-article/.premium/why-israel-isnt-sorry-it-never-stood-by-ukraine-against-russia/0000018d-e623-d7f4-a3dd-e62f0fdb0000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡为何缺席以色列地方选举活动</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-27/ty-article/.premium/why-netanyahu-is-absent-from-israels-local-election-campaigns/0000018d-e982-d1e0-a1dd-f9f79b810000</link><description>在国家层面上，地方选举很少能表明政治风向，尤其是在今年预计投票率异常低的情况下。但在战争期间举行选举仍然是以色列民主的一项成就</description><pubDate>Tue, 27 Feb 2024 10:15:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-27/ty-article/.premium/why-netanyahu-is-absent-from-israels-local-election-campaigns/0000018d-e982-d1e0-a1dd-f9f79b810000</guid></item><item><title>由于公众冷漠和加沙战争拖延，以色列人在地方选举中投票</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-27/ty-article/.premium/israelis-to-vote-in-local-elections-amid-public-apathy-and-gaza-war-delay/0000018d-e73c-db28-afdf-fffc64e00000</link><description>投票站早上 7 点开放，晚上 10 点关闭 ■ 预计投票率较低 ■ 由于缺席选票较多，最终结果将在选举后约五天左右公布 ■ 战斗中的以色列士兵将在加沙境内投票条</description><pubDate>Tue, 27 Feb 2024 04:00:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-27/ty-article/.premium/israelis-to-vote-in-local-elections-amid-public-apathy-and-gaza-war-delay/0000018d-e73c-db28-afdf-fffc64e00000</guid></item><item><title>以色列国防军承认黎巴嫩边境附近的基地遭到反坦克导弹袭击；火箭弹袭击以色列南部</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-27/ty-article-live/biden-sets-march-4-target-for-gaza-truce-mossad-chief-delaying-aid-risks-hostage-deal/0000018d-e888-d1e0-a1dd-f9fd39400000</link><description>最近的袭击中，以色列北部发射了约 20 枚火箭弹 ■ 拜登表示，他希望下周之前能够达成停火协议 ■ 哈马斯卫生部称，加沙地带昨天有 96 人死亡 ■ 消息人士称，哈马斯正在研究涉及 40 人的巴黎停火提案为期一天的停火和人质交换 ■ 以色列国防军在西岸杀死三名巴勒斯坦武装人员 ■ 巴勒斯坦总理提交辞职，将领导巴勒斯坦权力机构过渡政府</description><pubDate>Tue, 27 Feb 2024 03:13:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-27/ty-article-live/biden-sets-march-4-target-for-gaza-truce-mossad-chief-delaying-aid-risks-hostage-deal/0000018d-e888-d1e0-a1dd-f9fd39400000</guid></item><item><title>辛贝特警告犯罪分子已渗透到以色列-阿拉伯理事会，建议推迟地方选举</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-27/ty-article/.premium/shin-bet-warns-criminal-gangs-have-infiltrated-israeli-arab-councils/0000018d-e7e3-d7f4-a3dd-e7efd89e0000</link><description>发给内政部的秘密文件称，犯罪团伙在七个城市占据要职，并警告他们可能获得大量武器和爆炸物</description><pubDate>Tue, 27 Feb 2024 00:26:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-27/ty-article/.premium/shin-bet-warns-criminal-gangs-have-infiltrated-israeli-arab-councils/0000018d-e7e3-d7f4-a3dd-e7efd89e0000</guid></item><item><title>右翼非政府组织向巴勒斯坦活动人士道歉，称其与恐怖分子住在同一所房子里</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-27/ty-article/.premium/rightist-ngo-to-apologize-to-palestinian-activist-for-saying-he-lived-in-terrorists-home/0000018d-e7be-d05b-addd-e7bfe4190000</link><description>Ad Kan 在 Facebook 上谎称 Issa Amro 是 2001 年谋杀以色列婴儿 Shalhevet Pass 的男子的亲戚</description><pubDate>Mon, 26 Feb 2024 23:45:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-27/ty-article/.premium/rightist-ngo-to-apologize-to-palestinian-activist-for-saying-he-lived-in-terrorists-home/0000018d-e7be-d05b-addd-e7bfe4190000</guid></item><item><title>以色列证实：国家支付内塔尼亚胡私人游泳池的战时维修费用</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-27/ty-article/.premium/israel-confirms-state-paid-for-war-time-repairs-on-netanyahus-private-swimming-pool/0000018d-e73b-db28-afdf-fffbcce80000</link><description>在《国土报》发表报道后，总理办公室的法律顾问写道，部分修复工作已经完成，而其他请求则被审计长拒绝——审计长已辞职</description><pubDate>Mon, 26 Feb 2024 23:10:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-27/ty-article/.premium/israel-confirms-state-paid-for-war-time-repairs-on-netanyahus-private-swimming-pool/0000018d-e73b-db28-afdf-fffbcce80000</guid></item></channel></rss>